    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a pristine example of BMW M\u2019s engineering pinnacle. Powered by the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, the powerplant delivers linear torque and a visceral induction note. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. This chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS overhaul to ensure structural and mechanical integrity. The suspension maintains its factory-spec damping profile, and the exterior retains its original deep-gloss finish with zero oxidation. A collector-grade specimen for the driver who demands mechanical purity.",
