    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, meticulously maintained to satisfy the most discerning collector. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with zero imperfections, rock chips, or swirl marks, having been strictly garage-kept and protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is flawless; the premium leather remains supple and taut without a single crease or sign of wear, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component and driver-assist feature functions exactly as it did the day it was delivered. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive, chronological folder of every service performed at the authorized dealership. It has never been driven in inclement weather, and the undercarriage is as pristine as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a turn-key masterpiece that requires absolutely nothing but a new owner who appreciates perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
