      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically flawless example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L atmospheric inline-six pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from a documented VANOS bulletproofing and rod bearing replacement. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip rear differential with zero whine. The chassis is structurally sound, featuring a proactive subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings throughout the multi-link rear suspension. With an unblemished undercarriage and a cooling system overhauled with an aluminum radiator, this vehicle maintains optimal operating temperatures even under load. This is a turn-key, collector-quality driver with impeccable throttle response and a perfectly balanced weight distribution.",
